Key Kubernetes Concepts
Cloud computing, containerization, and container orchestration are the most important trends in DevOps. Whether you‚Äôre a data scientist, software developer, or product manager, it‚Äôs good to know Docker and Kubernetes basics. Both technologies help you collaborate with others, deploy your projects, and increase your value to employers.
In this article we‚Äôll cover essential Kubernetes concepts. There are a lot of Kubernetes terms, which can make it intimidating. I‚Äôll help you make a mental model to speed your understanding of the technology.
